 \int_1^{\infty} x^{\lambda}dx \; = \; -\frac{1}{\lambda + k} 
 \sum_{k = 1}^{n} \frac{\phi^{(k - 1)}(0)}{(k - 1)! (\lambda + k)} \; = \; \sum_{k = 1}^{n} \frac{-\phi^{(k - 1)}(0)}{(k - 1)!} \int_1^{\infty} x^{\lambda + k - 1} dx 
 \int_1^\infty x^\lambda \phi(x) dx \; + \; \sum_{k = 1}^n \frac{\phi^{(k - 1)}(0)}{(k - 1)! (\lambda + k)} \; = \; \int_1^{\infty} x^{\lambda} \left[ \phi(x) - \sum_{k = 1}^{n} \frac{\phi^{(k - 1)}(0) \, x^{k - 1}}{(k - 1)!} \right] dx 
